{"word":"G4389 - προτρέπομαι - protrépomai - prot-rep'-om-ahee - Exhort","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προτρέπομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">protrépomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prot-rep'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Exhort</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எச்சரி"},{"paragraph":"to urge forward, exhort, encourage"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; to <i>turn forward</i> for oneself, that is, <i>encourage:</i> - exhort.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}